WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:00.580 --> 00:00:01.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[engines revving]</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:02.250 --> 00:00:03.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like we made it!</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:04.170 --> 00:00:05.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have we really?</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:05.550 --> 00:00:08.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NENE] Yeah.
Nothing but green all around.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:08.340 --> 00:00:09.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
This is our front yard.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:11.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS]
Your what? Get out!</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:12.050 --> 00:00:14.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen stadiums
smaller than your yard!</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:14.810 --> 00:00:16.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[brakes squealing]</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:17.230 --> 00:00:18.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on just a sec.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:18.890 --> 00:00:21.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You could've told us you owned
a whole manor, you know?</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:23.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just our vacation home.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:23.900 --> 00:00:25.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Lou Erz.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:25.650 --> 00:00:27.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL]
What?</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:28.780 --> 00:00:30.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] How many of my rooms
do you think would fit in here?</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:31.660 --> 00:00:32.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
Don't ask that.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:32.910 --> 00:00:34.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ELLETEAR] There you are!
-[ALL] Huh?</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:37.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome all!
So glad you could make it.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:38.460 --> 00:00:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The manor awaits!</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:39.830 --> 00:00:41.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, make yourselves
at home.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:41.670 --> 00:00:42.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:43.630 --> 00:00:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>LINE OF DESCENT: THREE-SISTER
WAR (AKA ALICE HAS HAD ENOUGH)</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:44.340 --> 00:00:47.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unwind to your heart's content,
and have a pleasant stay.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:49.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON]
Mongrel soldiers.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:00:49.930 --> 00:00:53.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How nice of you to willingly
step into my trap.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:00:53.140 --> 00:00:54.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, face me!</b></Default>

c0000025
00:00:54.760 --> 00:00:56.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-[MISMIS] That voice!</b></Default>

c0000026
00:00:56.270 --> 00:00:57.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
The Masked Lord!</b></Default>

c0000027
00:00:57.720 --> 00:00:58.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is this, an ambush?</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:02.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No activity outside.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:02.690 --> 00:01:03.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All clear here.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:03.900 --> 00:01:06.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.
Was that you, Elletear?</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:07.230 --> 00:01:09.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So maybe I went a tad overboard</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:09.440 --> 00:01:11.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with introducing my skill
to our guests.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:11.910 --> 00:01:13.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[chuckles]
-[ALL] Ugh!</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:13.780 --> 00:01:16.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, really? Were none
of you lot entertained?</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:16.580 --> 00:01:18.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Weren't you dying
to know my power?</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:19.040 --> 00:01:21.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That voice is part
of your astral art?</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:23.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, aren't you the sharp one?</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:23.790 --> 00:01:26.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Much like a parrot mimicking
the voice of its owner.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:27.050 --> 00:01:28.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The astral ability I possess</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:28.550 --> 00:01:31.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is truly one of the most
useless within our kingdom.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:01:31.510 --> 00:01:32.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm-hm.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:01:32.590 --> 00:01:35.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now that we're all
very aware of my little talent,</b></Default>

c0000043
00:01:35.850 --> 00:01:37.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>rest easy, as honored guests.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:40.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My astral art cannot
even harm a baby.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:01:40.980 --> 00:01:42.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Self-deprecation, huh?</b></Default>

c0000046
00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:45.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Precisely.
Nothing more, nothing less.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:01:45.310 --> 00:01:47.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, I'm proud
to claim this ability</b></Default>

c0000048
00:01:47.770 --> 00:01:50.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as my own,
and I mean that, truly.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:51.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bell ringing]</b></Default>

c0000050
00:01:53.780 --> 00:01:55.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I almost forgot!</b></Default>

c0000051
00:01:55.780 --> 00:01:58.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must meet the servants
to the House of Lou.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:01:58.160 --> 00:02:00.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yumilecia, Cystea, Nami,</b></Default>

c0000053
00:02:00.660 --> 00:02:01.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ashe, and Noel.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:02:01.870 --> 00:02:04.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They will take care
of your every need.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:06.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000056
00:02:06.540 --> 00:02:08.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whispering]
They're all astral mages,</b></Default>

c0000057
00:02:08.550 --> 00:02:10.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but none of them possess
aggressive astral power.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:02:11.550 --> 00:02:13.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So they're not doubling
as bodyguards?</b></Default>

c0000059
00:02:13.970 --> 00:02:15.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It isn't normal
for someone to be both</b></Default>

c0000060
00:02:15.470 --> 00:02:16.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a servant and a bodyguard.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:02:17.890 --> 00:02:19.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not everyone's special
like Rin.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:22.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Rin. Is she hiding?</b></Default>

c0000063
00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:25.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure she must've been
able to tail us.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:02:26.100 --> 00:02:27.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

c0000065
00:02:27.810 --> 00:02:28.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:02:29.230 --> 00:02:30.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will Alice be here, too?</b></Default>

c0000067
00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:33.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, of course, she wouldn't be.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:02:33.950 --> 00:02:35.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[NAMI] Everyone.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000069
00:02:35.610 --> 00:02:37.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your rooms
are all ready for you now.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:02:37.820 --> 00:02:39.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You lot follow us.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:02:39.280 --> 00:02:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But before we go.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:02:40.700 --> 00:02:42.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All your weaponry and devices</b></Default>

c0000073
00:02:42.500 --> 00:02:44.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will be left
in our stewardship.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:02:44.710 --> 00:02:46.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[all gasp]
-[groans]</b></Default>

c0000075
00:02:46.460 --> 00:02:47.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We couldn't enjoy this vacation</b></Default>

c0000076
00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:50.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with such distractions,
now could we?</b></Default>

c0000077
00:02:51.130 --> 00:02:52.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ALL] Hm.
-[guns clicking]</b></Default>

c0000078
00:02:52.970 --> 00:02:55.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though you're
hateful Imperial soldiers,</b></Default>

c0000079
00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we invite you here
as honored guests.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:02:57.550 --> 00:02:59.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only because of
our Lady Elletear's orders.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:01.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL]
Ugh!</b></Default>

c0000082
00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:02.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Manners!</b></Default>

c0000083
00:03:02.980 --> 00:03:05.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ashe, that is no way to talk
to our distinguished company.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:03:06.060 --> 00:03:07.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't be so rude.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:03:07.310 --> 00:03:08.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ASHE]
Forgive me.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:03:08.610 --> 00:03:09.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And whatever you do,</b></Default>

c0000087
00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:11.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>mixing mud
into their coffee is a no-no.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:03:12.150 --> 00:03:14.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one was thinking that
until you said it!</b></Default>

c0000089
00:03:14.900 --> 00:03:17.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mud's messy!
Make sure it's detergent.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:03:17.910 --> 00:03:19.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that'd be even worse!</b></Default>

c0000091
00:03:19.910 --> 00:03:20.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[engine revving]</b></Default>

c0000092
00:03:20.870 --> 00:03:22.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
I can't let him know.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:03:22.790 --> 00:03:24.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About my dark secret.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:03:24.580 --> 00:03:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000095
00:03:27.960 --> 00:03:30.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Better look around
for glass shards or something.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:33.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Better safe than slicey.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:03:33.510 --> 00:03:34.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[knocking on door]</b></Default>

c0000098
00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:35.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000099
00:03:35.880 --> 00:03:37.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska.
Is everything okay?</b></Default>

c0000100
00:03:38.390 --> 00:03:39.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Think so.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:03:39.470 --> 00:03:40.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came to check on you.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:03:41.140 --> 00:03:42.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000103
00:03:43.060 --> 00:03:44.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing?</b></Default>

c0000104
00:03:44.390 --> 00:03:46.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]
Good, bed seems to be clear.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:48.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
From what?</b></Default>

c0000106
00:03:48.270 --> 00:03:49.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hidden communications.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:03:49.940 --> 00:03:51.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly,
I'm a little impressed</b></Default>

c0000108
00:03:51.480 --> 00:03:53.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to see you so
on the ball, Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:03:54.320 --> 00:03:55.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
I need to be!</b></Default>

c0000110
00:03:55.940 --> 00:03:57.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Always gotta stay alert.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:03:58.200 --> 00:03:59.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But why bug my room?</b></Default>

c0000112
00:03:59.910 --> 00:04:00.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Plenty of reasons.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:03.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For instance, to capture
the exact moment</b></Default>

c0000114
00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:05.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I reveal the Sovereignty's
many secrets to you.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:04:06.370 --> 00:04:09.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, wouldn't that be
a pretty easy job for Elletear?</b></Default>

c0000116
00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's like a walking
voice recorder.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:04:12.340 --> 00:04:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Technically, she's more
like an impersonator.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:04:15.170 --> 00:04:16.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's able to speak
in the voice of those</b></Default>

c0000119
00:04:16.970 --> 00:04:18.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>whom she's heard in the past.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:04:18.930 --> 00:04:19.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which means...</b></Default>

c0000121
00:04:20.260 --> 00:04:22.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she could make me say anything?</b></Default>

c0000122
00:04:22.550 --> 00:04:24.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yep.
Pretty much.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:26.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A lotta things get sorta gray</b></Default>

c0000124
00:04:26.310 --> 00:04:28.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when considering her ability
for evidence.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:04:28.640 --> 00:04:30.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-But enough about that!</b></Default>

c0000126
00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:32.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here!
We've got some work to do!</b></Default>

c0000127
00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:35.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Comms to find and Elletear's
plot to foil! -Wait!</b></Default>

c0000128
00:04:35.150 --> 00:04:36.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000129
00:04:36.900 --> 00:04:38.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right this way!</b></Default>

c0000130
00:04:40.070 --> 00:04:43.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] No doubt about it.
This is definitely your room.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:04:44.080 --> 00:04:45.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Like it?</b></Default>

c0000132
00:04:45.620 --> 00:04:47.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I painted it two years ago.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:04:47.870 --> 00:04:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You're kidding?
-[SISBELL] Are you surprised?</b></Default>

c0000134
00:04:50.250 --> 00:04:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've got the makings
of a pro, Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:04:52.580 --> 00:04:53.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000136
00:04:54.130 --> 00:04:56.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] Elletear's room
is up ahead. Come on.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:04:57.460 --> 00:04:58.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Isn't this a photograph?</b></Default>

c0000138
00:04:59.630 --> 00:05:01.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The picture of class.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:05:01.130 --> 00:05:03.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unmatchable beauty,
top education.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:05.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's everything
you would want in a queen.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:05:06.640 --> 00:05:08.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If she had
a powerful astral spirit,</b></Default>

c0000142
00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:10.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she would've been
next in line, hands down.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:05:11.480 --> 00:05:13.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] But I thought
all descendants of the Founder</b></Default>

c0000144
00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:14.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were powerful mages.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:16.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Elletear is an exception.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:05:18.190 --> 00:05:20.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But watch out.
She is extremely cunning.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:05:20.990 --> 00:05:22.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Best to stay on your guard
while around her.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:05:23.740 --> 00:05:25.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[latch clacking]</b></Default>

c0000149
00:05:25.660 --> 00:05:27.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, she keeps
her door locked.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:05:27.540 --> 00:05:28.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Private as ever.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:05:29.250 --> 00:05:30.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No luck here.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:05:30.290 --> 00:05:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go check Alice's room.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:33.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice's room, too?</b></Default>

c0000154
00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
We share the same wall.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:05:35.500 --> 00:05:38.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't think of a better place
to tap into my chamber.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:05:38.510 --> 00:05:39.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, let's go.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:05:39.800 --> 00:05:42.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000158
00:05:42.550 --> 00:05:43.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
This is it.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:46.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is that?</b></Default>

c0000160
00:05:46.930 --> 00:05:48.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
That's Alice's self-portrait.</b></Default>

c0000161
