00:11:38.990 --> 00:11:40.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're not here
on reconnaissance.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:11:41.160 --> 00:11:42.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, please.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:11:42.200 --> 00:11:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As if I'd allow you
to stir up any trouble.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:11:44.620 --> 00:11:46.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not while I'm here, you won't.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:11:47.500 --> 00:11:49.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm duty-bound.
As a princess.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:11:51.210 --> 00:11:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, promise me this.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:11:53.510 --> 00:11:56.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Keep your head down and do not
interfere with our nation.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:11:57.090 --> 00:11:58.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And don't try to escape.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:12:01.890 --> 00:12:03.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ASHE] Lady Alice?
-[both gasp]</b></Default>

c0000331
00:12:03.640 --> 00:12:05.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, what is it, Ashe?</b></Default>

c0000332
00:12:05.480 --> 00:12:06.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ASHE]
Is Iska with you?</b></Default>

c0000333
00:12:07.770 --> 00:12:09.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[BOTH] Hm?
-[ASHE] My lady has requested</b></Default>

c0000334
00:12:09.520 --> 00:12:10.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bring him to her.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:12.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that so?</b></Default>

c0000336
00:12:13.190 --> 00:12:14.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:12:14.690 --> 00:12:16.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Iska.
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000338
00:12:16.650 --> 00:12:18.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't trust a word
from Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:12:19.410 --> 00:12:22.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're my rival.
And mine alone.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:12:25.750 --> 00:12:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[door opens]
-Please, enter.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:12:27.410 --> 00:12:29.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Elletear.
You requested me?</b></Default>

c0000342
00:12:30.380 --> 00:12:32.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
I did! Do come in.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:12:35.880 --> 00:12:38.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you so much
for stopping by.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:12:38.630 --> 00:12:39.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:12:39.930 --> 00:12:41.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Oh, I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:12:42.260 --> 00:12:44.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You caught me
stepping out of the bath.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:12:45.430 --> 00:12:48.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000348
00:12:48.350 --> 00:12:49.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

c0000349
00:12:53.480 --> 00:12:54.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
I'll cut to the chase.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:12:54.780 --> 00:12:56.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm looking for comrades.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:12:56.780 --> 00:12:58.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one from the Sovereignty
will fight with me</b></Default>

c0000352
00:12:58.610 --> 00:13:01.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the same cause,
so I'm widening my net.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:13:02.120 --> 00:13:05.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And who better to recruit
to my team...than you,</b></Default>

c0000354
00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:06.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a one-time Saint Disciple?</b></Default>

c0000355
00:13:07.540 --> 00:13:08.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Recruit?</b></Default>

c0000356
00:13:08.830 --> 00:13:11.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like for you to be
my personal soldier.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:13:12.880 --> 00:13:14.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not following.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:13:14.500 --> 00:13:15.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why choose me?</b></Default>

c0000359
00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:17.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A loyalist would kill
for this chance.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:13:18.970 --> 00:13:21.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because I wish to annihilate
the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:13:21.680 --> 00:13:22.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000362
00:13:22.640 --> 00:13:24.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll raze every city
to the ground,</b></Default>

c0000363
00:13:24.930 --> 00:13:26.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wiping out the entire nation.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:13:27.850 --> 00:13:29.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well?
Doesn't that sound lovely?</b></Default>

c0000365
00:13:30.690 --> 00:13:32.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh! A rebellion?</b></Default>

c0000366
00:13:33.270 --> 00:13:35.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Traitor. You're the Queen's
own daughter,</b></Default>

c0000367
00:13:35.230 --> 00:13:36.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how could you?</b></Default>

c0000368
00:13:37.030 --> 00:13:39.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Did I scare you, hm?
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000369
00:13:39.610 --> 00:13:41.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Me, the first princess,</b></Default>

c0000370
00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:43.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wouldn't dare to dream
of something so outrageous.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I called you here
out of curiosity.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:13:48.250 --> 00:13:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't expect
a Saint Disciple</b></Default>

c0000373
00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:51.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to break a witch out of prison.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:13:52.080 --> 00:13:53.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you've looked into me?</b></Default>

c0000375
00:13:54.290 --> 00:13:56.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A while back, I caught wind
of an odd duck</b></Default>

c0000376
00:13:56.750 --> 00:13:58.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the Imperial Army,</b></Default>

c0000377
00:13:58.380 --> 00:14:01.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a soldier known
as the Anti-War Berserker.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:14:01.470 --> 00:14:03.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They plan to capture
a pureblood</b></Default>

c0000379
00:14:03.090 --> 00:14:05.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the Sovereignty
and force a peace treaty.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:14:06.310 --> 00:14:08.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It's you, is it not?
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000381
00:14:09.520 --> 00:14:11.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] She isn't supposed
to know about that.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:14:11.770 --> 00:14:13.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only a select few do, so how?</b></Default>

c0000383
00:14:14.810 --> 00:14:16.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did someone
from the Empire tell her?</b></Default>

c0000384
00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:18.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If so, then who?</b></Default>

c0000385
00:14:19.030 --> 00:14:20.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bell ringing]</b></Default>

c0000386
00:14:20.900 --> 00:14:22.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's 11 o'clock.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:14:22.610 --> 00:14:24.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That bell means
it's time to retire.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:14:25.370 --> 00:14:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does that mean our conversation
is over, as well?</b></Default>

c0000389
00:14:28.290 --> 00:14:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for being
quick to understand.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:14:32.040 --> 00:14:34.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[door creaks]
-[ELLETEAR] This way, please.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:14:35.710 --> 00:14:37.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Uh, what's the meaning of this?</b></Default>

c0000392
00:14:37.710 --> 00:14:40.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Leaving a defenseless woman
all by herself?</b></Default>

c0000393
00:14:40.590 --> 00:14:43.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't be so cruel.
I want a bodyguard.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:14:43.680 --> 00:14:44.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-huh.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:14:44.930 --> 00:14:46.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm asking you</b></Default>

c0000396
00:14:46.140 --> 00:14:48.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to sleep next to me
in bed for tonight.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:50.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Together?
Nope, I'm good!</b></Default>

c0000398
00:14:50.810 --> 00:14:53.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you forget that
I'm in the Imperial Army?</b></Default>

c0000399
00:14:53.140 --> 00:14:54.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Elletear laughs]</b></Default>

c0000400
00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:56.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That just makes this
even more exciting.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:14:57.110 --> 00:14:59.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A Saint Disciple
trembling at my touch?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:14:59.610 --> 00:15:00.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It drives me crazy.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:15:01.190 --> 00:15:02.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My heart's absolutely racing!</b></Default>

c0000404
00:15:03.280 --> 00:15:05.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-Here. You wanna feel?</b></Default>

c0000405
00:15:06.490 --> 00:15:07.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[door opens]
-Stop!</b></Default>

c0000406
00:15:07.950 --> 00:15:09.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think you're doing?</b></Default>

c0000407
00:15:09.410 --> 00:15:10.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Enjoying myself.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:15:11.160 --> 00:15:12.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what's that
supposed to mean?</b></Default>

c0000409
00:15:12.960 --> 00:15:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm on to you!</b></Default>

c0000410
00:15:14.540 --> 00:15:16.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you talking about?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't play dumb!
You're trying to steal my Iska!</b></Default>

c0000412
00:15:19.090 --> 00:15:20.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait! "Your Iska?"</b></Default>

c0000413
00:15:20.750 --> 00:15:21.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's so cute!</b></Default>

c0000414
00:15:22.050 --> 00:15:24.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if I'm the one
who invited him,</b></Default>

c0000415
00:15:24.090 --> 00:15:26.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then doesn't that mean
he's mine, sister?</b></Default>

c0000416
00:15:26.930 --> 00:15:28.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is going on?</b></Default>

c0000417
00:15:28.680 --> 00:15:30.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The man you invited
happens to be my guard!</b></Default>

c0000418
00:15:31.180 --> 00:15:32.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The only person
who has the right</b></Default>

c0000419
00:15:32.390 --> 00:15:33.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to sleep with him
is me, got it?</b></Default>

c0000420
00:15:34.060 --> 00:15:35.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
No, you don't!</b></Default>

c0000421
00:15:35.390 --> 00:15:37.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
Adorable!</b></Default>

c0000422
00:15:37.730 --> 00:15:40.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just hearing you talk back. Aw.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:15:40.320 --> 00:15:42.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what does my baby sister
want, a head pat?</b></Default>

c0000424
00:15:42.940 --> 00:15:44.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be told she's a big girl?</b></Default>

c0000425
00:15:44.700 --> 00:15:46.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is enough!</b></Default>

c0000426
00:15:46.910 --> 00:15:49.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing in here,
and why is Iska with you?</b></Default>

c0000427
00:15:49.990 --> 00:15:51.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOTH]
We're sleeping with him.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:15:51.910 --> 00:15:53.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sleeping with...?</b></Default>

c0000429
00:15:53.250 --> 00:15:55.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you guys even hear
yourselves right now?</b></Default>

c0000430
00:15:56.080 --> 00:15:58.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No! No one's sleeping with him!</b></Default>

c0000431
00:15:58.920 --> 00:16:00.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do I detect jealousy?</b></Default>

c0000432
00:16:00.540 --> 00:16:03.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Over a man who is nothing
but a stranger to you, Alice?</b></Default>

c0000433
00:16:03.590 --> 00:16:05.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You do know he's
an Imperial soldier, right?</b></Default>

c0000434
00:16:06.010 --> 00:16:08.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, I'm well aware
he's from the Army!</b></Default>

c0000435
00:16:08.300 --> 00:16:10.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's mine!
Wait, I mean,</b></Default>

c0000436
00:16:10.680 --> 00:16:12.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it makes more sense
if we share a bed!</b></Default>

c0000437
00:16:12.680 --> 00:16:14.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That way, he's within my sight!</b></Default>

c0000438
00:16:14.430 --> 00:16:15.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks, but no thanks.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:16:15.810 --> 00:16:17.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to stay in my room,</b></Default>

c0000440
00:16:17.270 --> 00:16:18.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if it's all the same to you.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:16:18.690 --> 00:16:20.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My bed is big enough
for the four of us.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:16:20.860 --> 00:16:22.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's comfort you're
worried about, don't be.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:16:22.980 --> 00:16:24.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-That sound fair to everyone?
-Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:27.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-No objections from me.
-Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:16:27.360 --> 00:16:29.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I, for one, completely object!</b></Default>

c0000446
00:16:29.700 --> 00:16:31.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anybody listening?</b></Default>

c0000447
00:16:32.700 --> 00:16:34.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To keep things fair,
we'll draw.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:16:35.040 --> 00:16:37.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska will sleep on
the far-left side of the bed,</b></Default>

c0000449
00:16:37.750 --> 00:16:39.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we can determine our order.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:16:40.460 --> 00:16:41.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right, I'll go first.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:16:42.960 --> 00:16:44.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Boo. I'm in the middle.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:46.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm on the right side.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:16:47.260 --> 00:16:48.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
I did it!</b></Default>

c0000454
00:16:48.630 --> 00:16:51.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yay! I got the spot
next to Iska!</b></Default>

c0000455
00:16:51.180 --> 00:16:52.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[laughing]
-[SISBELL] Alice?</b></Default>

c0000456
00:16:52.260 --> 00:16:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.
[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000457
00:16:53.890 --> 00:16:55.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, I know you cheated!</b></Default>

c0000458
00:16:55.470 --> 00:16:57.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I order you
to give up your spot!</b></Default>

c0000459
00:16:57.350 --> 00:16:59.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Nice try, but not happening!</b></Default>

c0000460
00:16:59.520 --> 00:17:00.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000461
00:17:05.610 --> 00:17:07.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way I can sleep.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:17:08.110 --> 00:17:09.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Alice?
-Shh.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:17:09.820 --> 00:17:10.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:17:12.370 --> 00:17:14.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be quiet.
And listen.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:17:15.200 --> 00:17:18.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever happens, I have
my royal seat to think about.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:17:18.250 --> 00:17:20.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Skin-to-skin contact
with a princess is forbidden.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:17:21.040 --> 00:17:23.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine by me. I wasn't planning
on doing anything.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:17:24.130 --> 00:17:25.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ELLETEAR] Oh, my.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000469
00:17:25.630 --> 00:17:26.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Your cheeks are much softer</b></Default>

c0000470
00:17:27.010 --> 00:17:28.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than I expected
them to be, Iska.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:17:28.840 --> 00:17:31.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
You're so handsy, Iska.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:17:31.510 --> 00:17:33.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's not like I wanted
you to hug me or anything.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:17:33.970 --> 00:17:36.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Oh, gosh! I'm so sorry!</b></Default>

c0000474
00:17:36.470 --> 00:17:38.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, you're fine,
it's just that...</b></Default>

c0000475
00:17:38.310 --> 00:17:40.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Can you back up?
-Huh.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:17:40.350 --> 00:17:41.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Getting a little tight.</b></Default>

c0000477
00:17:41.810 --> 00:17:43.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm. I would if I could,</b></Default>

c0000478
00:17:43.440 --> 00:17:46.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but Sisbell's kicking me!
I can't move.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:17:46.690 --> 00:17:48.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kicking in her sleep?</b></Default>

c0000480
00:17:48.610 --> 00:17:49.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000481
00:17:51.280 --> 00:17:52.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
She's so close.</b></Default>

c0000482
00:17:52.820 --> 00:17:54.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can feel her breath.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:17:54.320 --> 00:17:57.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000484
00:17:57.700 --> 00:17:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Why are you touching?</b></Default>

c0000485
00:17:59.330 --> 00:18:00.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Wow.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:18:01.040 --> 00:18:02.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're pretty toned.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:18:02.170 --> 00:18:04.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would've never guessed that
by looking at you.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:18:04.880 --> 00:18:08.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, um, what happened to
no skin-on-skin contact, huh?</b></Default>

c0000489
00:18:08.670 --> 00:18:10.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This doesn't count,
I'm trapped here!</b></Default>

c0000490
00:18:11.130 --> 00:18:14.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, you're covered up,
so there's no skin-on-skin.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:18:15.300 --> 00:18:16.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's your turn.</b></Default>

c0000492
00:18:17.180 --> 00:18:18.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see you staring.</b></Default>

c0000493
00:18:19.270 --> 00:18:20.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't mind.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:18:20.980 --> 00:18:22.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice...</b></Default>

c0000495
00:18:22.100 --> 00:18:24.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] It wouldn't be fair
if you didn't touch me.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:18:24.810 --> 00:18:27.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I did reach
out to you first.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:18:28.650 --> 00:18:29.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now's your chance.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:18:30.030 --> 00:18:32.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You might not get another
opportunity like this one.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:18:32.650 --> 00:18:34.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine.
I'm allowing it.</b></Default>

c0000500
00:18:35.160 --> 00:18:36.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're making me feel
like a perv!</b></Default>

c0000501
00:18:37.740 --> 00:18:39.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I said I wanted
to fight you</b></Default>

c0000502
00:18:39.240 --> 00:18:40.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fair and square, I meant it.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:18:41.710 --> 00:18:43.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In any situation.</b></Default>

c0000504
00:18:44.290 --> 00:18:45.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000505
00:18:45.540 --> 00:18:52.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000506
00:18:53.010 --> 00:18:54.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait.
That's right.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:18:54.840 --> 00:18:55.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, what is it?</b></Default>

c0000508
00:18:56.470 --> 00:18:58.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You saw.
-Saw what?</b></Default>

c0000509
00:18:58.970 --> 00:19:00.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My darkest secret.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:19:00.680 --> 00:19:01.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you touched them.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:19:02.140 --> 00:19:04.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was a misunderstanding!</b></Default>

c0000512
00:19:04.390 --> 00:19:05.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Misunderstanding or not,</b></Default>

c0000513
00:19:06.270 --> 00:19:07.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as your rival,</b></Default>

c0000514
00:19:07.440 --> 00:19:08.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's only fair
that I get to peek</b></Default>

c0000515
00:19:08.980 --> 00:19:10.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at your underwear, too!</b></Default>

c0000516
00:19:11.690 --> 00:19:13.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Wait!
What are you doing?</b></Default>

c0000517
00:19:13.820 --> 00:19:15.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm simply getting even!</b></Default>

c0000518
00:19:15.360 --> 00:19:16.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice!
[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000519
00:19:16.700 --> 00:19:18.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
S-O-S, Rin!</b></Default>

c0000520
00:19:18.410 --> 00:19:20.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your mistress
is currently losing it!</b></Default>

c0000521
00:19:20.540 --> 00:19:21.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, stop her!</b></Default>

c0000522
00:19:22.870 --> 00:19:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Did something good
happen yesterday, Lady Alice?</b></Default>

c0000523
00:19:25.580 --> 00:19:27.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your skin and hair
are positively glowing!</b></Default>

c0000524
00:19:28.170 --> 00:19:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000525
00:19:29.040 --> 00:19:31.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps sharing a bed with
my sisters livened my mood!</b></Default>

c0000526
00:19:32.010 --> 00:19:33.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[NENE] Nice shot!
-[BOTH] Hm?</b></Default>

c0000527
00:19:34.010 --> 00:19:35.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
All right.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:19:35.880 --> 00:19:37.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thwacks]
-[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000529
00:19:37.090 --> 00:19:39.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ISKA] What?
-[RIN] Color me surprised.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:19:39.100 --> 00:19:41.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Imperial swordsman
has a crappy golf hand.</b></Default>

c0000531
00:19:41.850 --> 00:19:43.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
This is so frustrating!</b></Default>

c0000532
00:19:43.770 --> 00:19:46.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I-I'd teach him if I was
down there right now!</b></Default>

c0000533
00:19:46.140 --> 00:19:47.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Let's fix your posture!
-[ALICE] Ah, Sisbell!</b></Default>

c0000534
00:19:47.860 --> 00:19:49.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I'll scold you later.
-[ISKA] Oh. Thanks, Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000535
00:19:49.690 --> 00:19:51.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Lady Alice, it's time.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:19:51.530 --> 00:19:52.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's time?</b></Default>

c0000537
00:19:52.820 --> 00:19:53.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you forgotten?</b></Default>

c0000538
00:19:54.280 --> 00:19:56.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Elletear will be returning
to the palace.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:19:59.530 --> 00:20:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[humming]</b></Default>

c0000540
00:20:00.780 --> 00:20:01.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:20:02.240 --> 00:20:03.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000542
00:20:03.620 --> 00:20:05.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've come to say goodbye,
baby sister.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:20:05.910 --> 00:20:07.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's do this again very soon.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:20:07.790 --> 00:20:08.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>E-Elletear?</b></Default>

c0000545
00:20:09.210 --> 00:20:11.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think of all the fun times
we two could have had</b></Default>

c0000546
00:20:11.380 --> 00:20:12.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you went out more often.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:20:12.750 --> 00:20:15.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're always cooped up with
your servant, it's a shame.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:20:15.800 --> 00:20:17.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-[ELLETEAR] Speaking of...</b></Default>

c0000549
00:20:17.300 --> 00:20:18.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[whimpering]
-[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000550
00:20:18.550 --> 00:20:20.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How have you been doing
since the old man's abduction?</b></Default>

c0000551
00:20:21.260 --> 00:20:22.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I imagine it's been so hard.</b></Default>

c0000552
00:20:23.020 --> 00:20:24.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000553
00:20:24.180 --> 00:20:26.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] Did she say
Schwartz was abducted?</b></Default>

c0000554
00:20:26.140 --> 00:20:27.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where's this coming from?</b></Default>

c0000555
00:20:27.770 --> 00:20:29.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's possible
he had an accident,</b></Default>

c0000556
00:20:29.440 --> 00:20:30.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or suddenly became ill.</b></Default>

c0000557
00:20:30.860 --> 00:20:32.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if I don't have
all the answers,</b></Default>

c0000558
00:20:32.320 --> 00:20:33.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then how can she be so sure?</b></Default>

c0000559
00:20:34.990 --> 00:20:38.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unless, she's the one behind
Schwartz's disappearance!</b></Default>

c0000560
00:20:38.320 --> 00:20:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sisbell whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000561
00:20:41.620 --> 00:20:42.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Which also means,</b></Default>

c0000562
00:20:43.330 --> 00:20:44.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the one who
betrayed the Lous...</b></Default>

c0000563
00:20:45.660 --> 00:20:47.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is you, Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000564
00:20:47.790 --> 00:20:49.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Cold, dear sister?</b></Default>

c0000565
00:20:49.250 --> 00:20:50.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're shaking like a leaf.</b></Default>

c0000566
00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:53.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's close the window
and stay inside.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:20:53.710 --> 00:20:55.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So long as you stay
right where you are</b></Default>

c0000568
00:20:55.800 --> 00:20:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>inside the manor,</b></Default>

c0000569
00:20:57.170 --> 00:20:59.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm certain Schwartz
will return to you.</b></Default>

c0000570
00:20:59.890 --> 00:21:00.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000571
00:21:04.180 --> 00:21:05.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Talisman grunts]</b></Default>

c0000572
00:21:05.270 --> 00:21:08.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The sun's timeless beauty
prevails even at night.</b></Default>

c0000573
00:21:08.770 --> 00:21:12.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now then...I believe
preparations are in order.</b></Default>

c0000574
00:21:12.900 --> 00:21:14.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON]
Word from the palace.</b></Default>

c0000575
00:21:14.320 --> 00:21:16.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems Elletear
has finally returned.</b></Default>

c0000576
00:21:17.150 --> 00:21:19.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] I was convinced
that when she was born,</b></Default>

c0000577
00:21:19.490 --> 00:21:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she could never become a Queen</b></Default>

c0000578
00:21:21.030 --> 00:21:23.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>through the fraudulent power
of impersonation.</b></Default>

c0000579
00:21:23.870 --> 00:21:26.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was certain the
House of Zoa would triumph.</b></Default>

c0000580
00:21:26.580 --> 00:21:28.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems we've been
outwitted, On.</b></Default>

c0000581
00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:31.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vexingly so.</b></Default>

c0000582
00:21:31.920 --> 00:21:34.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First, the House of Hydra
blows up the Queen's hall.</b></Default>

c0000583
00:21:34.800 --> 00:21:36.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then,
Elletear channels my voice</b></Default>

c0000584
00:21:36.710 --> 00:21:38.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the smoke and chaos.</b></Default>

c0000585
00:21:38.550 --> 00:21:40.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the perfect plot
to implicate me.</b></Default>

c0000586
00:21:41.300 --> 00:21:42.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Curious.</b></Default>

c0000587
00:21:42.680 --> 00:21:45.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For a brilliant woman to resort
to such aggression,</b></Default>

c0000588
00:21:45.140 --> 00:21:46.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't help but wonder</b></Default>

c0000589
00:21:46.270 --> 00:21:47.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if we're overlooking
the big picture.</b></Default>

c0000590
00:21:48.180 --> 00:21:49.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY]
You suspect there's more?</b></Default>

c0000591
00:21:50.060 --> 00:21:52.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suspect they haven't shown
their full hand.</b></Default>

c0000592
00:21:53.270 --> 00:21:54.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In which case, you, Kissing...</b></Default>

c0000593
00:21:55.770 --> 00:21:57.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should be ready
for what's to come.</b></Default>

c0000594
00:21:57.860 --> 00:21:59.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Within a few days' time.</b></Default>

c0000595
00:22:00.950 --> 00:22:02.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's gotta be the one
behind it, then.</b></Default>

c0000596
00:22:03.530 --> 00:22:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one who abducted
that old geezer is your sister.</b></Default>

c0000597
00:22:06.370 --> 00:22:07.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what're you
gonna do about it?</b></Default>

c0000598
00:22:08.040 --> 00:22:10.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be nice!
Don't call him that!</b></Default>

c0000599
00:22:10.750 --> 00:22:12.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Hm? Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000600
00:22:12.290 --> 00:22:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you think she outed
herself as the culprit to us?</b></Default>

c0000601
00:22:15.670 --> 00:22:16.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
To restrict Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000602
00:22:17.670 --> 00:22:20.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Basically telling her to be
a good prisoner and stay put.</b></Default>

c0000603
00:22:20.970 --> 00:22:22.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, what do you
want us to do?</b></Default>

c0000604
00:22:23.010 --> 00:22:23.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gun clacks]</b></Default>

c0000605
00:22:23.930 --> 00:22:25.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And why give us
our weapons back?</b></Default>

c0000606
00:22:26.390 --> 00:22:28.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll return home in eight days.</b></Default>

c0000607
00:22:28.390 --> 00:22:29.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, I will find
the one behind</b></Default>

c0000608
00:22:29.770 --> 00:22:32.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the assassination attempt
and be done with it.</b></Default>

c0000609
00:22:32.730 --> 00:22:33.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
That long?</b></Default>

c0000610
00:22:34.100 --> 00:22:35.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000611
00:22:35.190 --> 00:22:37.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anything can happen in the span
of eight days, correct?</b></Default>

c0000612
00:22:38.070 --> 00:22:39.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I'm saying is,
it's worth considering</b></Default>

c0000613
00:22:40.030 --> 00:22:41.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-who you're dealing with.
-[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000614
00:22:41.610 --> 00:22:43.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do your instincts
tell you?</b></Default>

c0000615
00:22:43.360 --> 00:22:45.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will Elletear make her move
between now and then?</b></Default>

c0000616
00:22:46.330 --> 00:22:47.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No doubt in my mind.</b></Default>

c0000617
00:22:48.080 --> 00:22:50.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be ready to hustle
to the palace, ya got it?</b></Default>

c0000618
00:22:51.330 --> 00:22:52.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is something going on?</b></Default>

c0000619
00:22:53.250 --> 00:22:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska and Sisbell still haven't
set foot outside their rooms.</b></Default>

c0000620
00:22:57.250 --> 00:22:59.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those two aren't
avoiding me, are they?</b></Default>

c0000621
00:22:59.840 --> 00:23:01.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's hope Iska stays away.</b></Default>

c0000622
00:23:01.550 --> 00:23:03.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the rest of his sad life.</b></Default>

c0000623
00:23:03.630 --> 00:23:05.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was around the time
Elletear left, too.</b></Default>

c0000624
00:23:06.550 --> 00:23:07.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't like this.</b></Default>

c0000625
00:23:08.180 --> 00:23:09.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[knife clanks]
-[RIN] Regarding your sister.</b></Default>

c0000626
00:23:10.310 --> 00:23:11.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There will be a hearing
in the Queen's hall</b></Default>

c0000627
00:23:12.060 --> 00:23:13.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at exactly 11 o'clock.</b></Default>

c0000628
00:23:14.810 --> 00:23:15.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[watch clanks]</b></Default>

c0000629
00:23:15.770 --> 00:23:17.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
It's about to start.</b></Default>

c0000630
00:23:18.070 --> 00:23:19.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000631
00:23:19.400 --> 00:23:22.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does the blanket of night
ever give you a sense of dread?</b></Default>

c0000632
00:23:22.860 --> 00:23:24.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not at all, Mother.</b></Default>

c0000633
00:23:24.530 --> 00:23:26.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you ask?
Are you afraid of the night?</b></Default>

c0000634
00:23:27.700 --> 00:23:29.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Perhaps a little bit.</b></Default>

c0000635
00:23:29.620 --> 00:23:30.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The older I grow,</b></Default>

c0000636
00:23:31.080 --> 00:23:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the more the whisper
from the evening wind</b></Default>

c0000637
00:23:33.040 --> 00:23:34.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>weakens me.</b></Default>

c0000638
00:23:34.920 --> 00:23:37.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come now, Mother, don't say
such depressing things.</b></Default>

c0000639
00:23:38.210 --> 00:23:40.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The people of the Sovereignty
are relying on you</b></Default>

c0000640
00:23:40.500 --> 00:23:41.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to remain their queen.</b></Default>

c0000641
00:23:42.050 --> 00:23:44.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My waning strength
doesn't sadden me as much</b></Default>

c0000642
00:23:45.380 --> 00:23:47.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as witnessing
my precious daughters</b></Default>

c0000643
00:23:47.180 --> 00:23:48.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>quarrel, like enemies.</b></Default>

c0000644
00:23:49.930 --> 00:23:51.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what breaks my heart.</b></Default>

c0000645
00:23:52.390 --> 00:23:53.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Answer me.</b></Default>

c0000646
00:23:53.680 --> 00:23:56.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why take Sisbell away
to the manor, Elletear?</b></Default>

c0000647
00:23:56.980 --> 00:23:57.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000648
00:23:57.980 --> 00:23:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] The explosion
of the Queen's hall.</b></Default>

c0000649
00:24:00.360 --> 00:24:01.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Framing the Zoa.</b></Default>

c0000650
00:24:02.400 --> 00:24:04.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You used your
astral power, didn't you?</b></Default>

c0000651
00:24:04.860 --> 00:24:06.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're speaking nonsense,
Mother!</b></Default>

c0000652
00:24:07.240 --> 00:24:10.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, how I truly want to believe
those eyes of yours, Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000653
00:24:10.950 --> 00:24:12.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I can't.</b></Default>

c0000654
00:24:12.160 --> 00:24:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
Mother.</b></Default>

c0000655
00:24:13.580 --> 00:24:15.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do me a favor,
and please let Sisbell know</b></Default>

c0000656
00:24:15.870 --> 00:24:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she can return
to the palace.</b></Default>

c0000657
00:24:18.040 --> 00:24:19.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm?
-[Elletear sighs]</b></Default>

c0000658
00:24:19.670 --> 00:24:21.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're right on schedule.</b></Default>

c0000659
00:24:21.670 --> 00:24:22.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[watch ticks]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000660
00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:24.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[rumbling]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000661
00:24:25.010 --> 00:24:26.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It cannot be!</b></Default>

c0000662
00:24:26.340 --> 00:24:28.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is happening?</b></Default>

